	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It's probably a brand thing... the card reader used in the PowerPak doesn't seem to like your CF card. It happens sometimes. Luckly, my 1GB CF card works fine with my PowerPak, and I didn't do anything special to it.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


